    "Data are quantities we observe (such as the previous portfolio weights) or forecast (such as return means, market volumes, or bid-ask spreads):",
    "• Pre-trade portfolio weights w pre and c pre.",
    "• Asset return forecast µ.",
    "• Risk model Σ, or for a factor model, F, Σ f, and D.",
    "• Holding cost parameters κ short and κ borrow."
